; Line types:
;   telnet  - Accept incoming TCP connections (default)
;   serial  - Use BlockDriver for modem/serial communication
;   local   - Desktop-only access via View/Logon buttons
;
; Serial options (required when type=serial):
;   driver  - BlockDriver module name (e.g., InternalPC, Dual, Atomwide)
;   port    - Port number for multi-port drivers (0-based)
;   speed   - Baud rate (300-115200)
;   format  - Word format: 8N1, 7E1, 7O1, 8E1, 8O1
;   flow    - Flow control: none, rts, xon
;

